product_name: e.l.f. CosmeticsSheer For It Blush Lip + Cheek Tint
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty Freee.l.f. Cosmetics' multi-use Sheer For It Blush Tint is a buildable stain for lips + cheeks with a watery texture that makes it easy as e.l.f. to blend and build up for a dreamy hint of color with a natural finish. Infused with Hyaluronic acid to deliver a surge of hydration to skin and lips.
details: DetailsBenefitsMulti-use lip & cheek tint for a sheer wash of colorHydrating watery texture delivers a natural flush finishLong-lasting, transfer-resistant stainBlendable & buildable formulae.l.f. is double-certified cruelty-free by Leaping Bunny & PETAe.l.f. is proud to partner with Fair Trade USA & manufacture products in Fair Trade Certified facilities; look for the Fair Trade Certified seal on your e.l.f. productKey IngredientsHyaluronic acidFormulated WithoutPhthalatesParabensNonylphenol ethoxylatesTriclosanTriclocarbanItem 2639512How To UseSwipe blush tint on cheeks with the applicator.Blend in a tapping motion using the e.l.f. Stain & Tint Blending Brush (sold separately).IngredientsOrange Crush: Water (Aqua), Glycerin, PPG-26-Buteth-26, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Phenoxyethanol, Hydroxyacetophenone, Diethylhexyl Syringylidenemalonate, Xanthan Gum, Hydrolyzed Sodium Hyaluronate, Caprylyl Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Disodium EDTA, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Citric Acid, Sodium Citrate. May Contain: Yellow 6 (CI 15985), Red 33 (CI 17200), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Red 40 (CI 16035).Ingredients may change or vary from time to time. Please refer to the packaging of the product you receive for the list of ingredients in your particular product.
how_to_use: Swipe blush tint on cheeks with the applicator.Blend in a tapping motion using the e.l.f. Stain & Tint Blending Brush (sold separately).

reviews.headline: Great color, even better product!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love how cute this little bottle is. It is very smooth and smells okay. It blends pretty well and overall is pigmented very well. I absolutely adore this color and have been loving incorporating it into my makeup routine.

reviews.headline: Great but not the best
reviews.comments: The product is good and lasts forever! Packaging is so cute and I love the big applicator! Pigment is STRONG so you will have to blend it fast!! But good overall!!!!

reviews.headline: love the applicator
reviews.comments: i love the scent. it's not too over baring. the texture is smooth which makes it easy to blend. the pigmentation was perfect for my complexion and the packaging is quality.

reviews.headline: Lightweight, blendable blush that gives a natural glow witho
reviews.comments: I really like the e.l.f. Sheer for It Blush Tint! The texture is lightweight and smooth, it blends easily into the skin, and the pigmentation is buildable without looking heavy. The packaging is cute and easy to use, plus it has a fresh, clean feel with no strong scent. Perfect for a natural everyday look that lasts for hours.

reviews.headline: Long lasting
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Sheer for It Blush Tint in Cherry Cola delivers a fresh, natural-looking flush that's perfect for everyday wear. The lightweight, gel-like formula blends seamlessly into the skin, giving a dewy, just-bitten look without feeling sticky or heavy. Cherry Cola offers a soft, muted berry tone that works well on a variety of skin tones, and its long-lasting, buildable coverage lets you go from subtle to more vibrant with ease. Ideal for a quick, effortless pop of color.

reviews.headline: The perfect NATURAL Flush
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This blush is such a fun and vibrant shade! It gives the cheeks a beautiful, natural flush. The packaging matches the shade + lil goes a long way! My tip: apply and blend one side at a time since it sets quickly, almost like a lip stain. It's perfect for a fresh, youthful glow that lasts throughout the day.

reviews.headline: I'll try my besy
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I am not going to lie. I don't know how to use blush tints or liquid blush at all. I don't even have a specific brush to blend it out. I tired my best to blend it. ðŸ˜‚ i did love the color so much and I prefer powders blush!

reviews.headline: Pretty
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Blends in beautifully and looks so natural because it's a stain! I use this every day over my foundation and it looks great. Use on top of makeup or alone

reviews.headline: Nice long lasting blush option!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Blush is quite pretty & definitely long lasting. It also absolutely lives up to the "sheer" title but it can be built up which I do appreciate. Photos show before and immediately after application, however I did wear this to work (office job) and it held up very well.

reviews.headline: Great stain
reviews.comments: I love how beautiful the stain is on my lips and I use it on my cheeks! I got a light pink color, but it looks pretty pink on my cheeks and lips. The stain lasts hours when I leave the house. So I don't need to reapply like normal lipstick. I like this!

reviews.headline: Pretty color
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is a good alternative to the dry powders. It blends much better due to its liquidity. I prefer zero scents due to allergies but it wasn't overpowering. I like the color as it goes well with my olive skin tone.

reviews.headline: Good pigment
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This tinted blush works pretty darn good, only thing I say is don't use your fingers to blend it. It definitely stains your skin for a little bit. The pigment is bright so, you don't need a lot of product. I liked that the product lasts all day, the color of this exact one wasn't my favorite, but I'll definitely give others a try.

reviews.headline: Love for lips
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love this product for my lips! It gives a very subtle tint to my lips and is beautiful. I cover it with aqua for and it didn't smudge. I tried it for my cheeks too and it worked well.

reviews.headline: Love it
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love any type of tints. This was such the perfect color for me. The pigmentation was perfect and fit my skin tone. It was also super blendable. Packaging was simple and easy.

reviews.headline: Beautiful color! No smear!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This lip and blush tint is awesome! I've never tried a stain before and fell in love with it so quickly! It dries fast, doesn't smudge, smear or leave residue on drinks/straws! Beautiful color and easy application

reviews.headline: Great!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is amazing as a blush! I think it's the right shade for me and and too over powering. It blends in sooo well! The lip part is also good, but I like it more as a blush.

reviews.headline: Cute color
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I tried  and while the color looks soft and natural, I don't really like the smell. It blends easily and feels light on the skin, but the scent is distracting for me.

reviews.headline: Love
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is a very pretty color, looks so high end and comparable to the benefit color tint. Use on your cheeks and lips for an easy application and color. I would for sure get to see elf products

reviews.headline: Love this I use it every day!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This color !! So good ! Love the easy application! Smells so good and feels great ! Packaging is perfect fits in my purse for all day touch ups! Love

reviews.headline: BENEFIT DUPE
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I am truly obsessed with this sheer tinted blush. It is just like a dupe for the benefit one, but I think this one is 1 million times better. It is so pigmented but blends really well with the brush. It lasts me all day and gives me a beautiful natural blush look.

faceoff_positive.comments: I have really enjoyed using the e.l.f. sheer for it blush tint. It is very similar to a popular brands product but for a much more reasonable price. While I tried it on my cheeks, I personally preferred using it on my lips. The coverage is amazing. It stayed nicely on my lips while eating and drinking. It slowly fades instead of wiping away. I love that it didn't clump up or cake and crack. Despite having dry lips, it still looked incredible. I thought it last a good amount of time. I highly recommend this product. While I received this product as a free sample in exchange for my review, these thoughts are my own and I will be repurchasing again on my own.
faceoff_positive.headline: Great Dupe, nice color

faceoff_negative.comments: I have freckles on my cheeks and this product did not like sticking to the areas around them, leading to patchy application. I also feel like it emphasized my pores by staining them darker than the rest of my skin However I work outdoors and this stain lasted 8 hours and withstood sweat and rubbing against my face buff. Worked pretty well on my lips but faded faster on them, probably lasted around 4 hours on my lips
faceoff_negative.headline: Freckle havers beware
